{"metadata":{"title":"UnifiedDI \/ DI API Quick Reference","modules":[{"name":"DiContainer"}],"role":"article","roleHeading":"Article"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/DiContainer\/documentation\/DiContainer\/UnifiedDI-DI-QuickReference","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"kind":"article","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"이 문서는 UnifiedDI와 DI의 핵심 사용 패턴을 한눈에 확인할 수 있는 요약 가이드입니다. 등록(Register) \/ 해결(Resolve) \/ 해제(Release) \/ 스코프(Scope) 사용법을 정리했습니다."}],"seeAlsoSections":[{"title":"API 참조","generated":true,"anchor":"API-참조","identifiers":["doc:\/\/DiContainer\/documentation\/DiContainer\/UnifiedDI","doc:\/\/DiContainer\/documentation\/DiContainer\/UnifiedDI\/registerMany(_:)","doc:\/\/DiContainer\/documentation\/DiContainer\/UnifiedDI\/registerScoped(_:scope:factory:)","doc:\/\/DiContainer\/documentation\/DiContainer\/UnifiedDI\/registerAsyncScoped(_:scope:factory:)","doc:\/\/DiContainer\/documentation\/DiContainer\/DI\/registerScoped(_:scope:factory:)","doc:\/\/DiContainer\/documentation\/DiContainer\/DI\/registerAsyncScoped(_:scope:factory:)","doc:\/\/DiContainer\/documentation\/DiContainer\/UnifiedDI","doc:\/\/DiContainer\/documentation\/DiContainer\/UnifiedDI","doc:\/\/DiContainer\/documentation\/DiContainer\/UnifiedDI\/resolveThrows(_:)","doc:\/\/DiContainer\/documentation\/DiContainer\/UnifiedDI\/resolve(_:default:)","doc:\/\/DiContainer\/documentation\/DiContainer\/DI\/resolve(_:)","doc:\/\/DiContainer\/documentation\/DiContainer\/DI\/resolveResult(_:)","doc:\/\/DiContainer\/documentation\/DiContainer\/DI\/resolveThrows(_:)","doc:\/\/DiContainer\/documentation\/DiContainer\/UnifiedDI\/release(_:)","doc:\/\/DiContainer\/documentation\/DiContainer\/UnifiedDI\/releaseAll()"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"UnifiedDI","anchor":"UnifiedDI"},{"level":3,"type":"heading","text":"등록(Registration)","anchor":"%EB%93%B1%EB%A1%9DRegistration"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["\/\/ 기본 등록","UnifiedDI.register(Service.self) { ServiceImpl() }","","\/\/ 조건부 등록","UnifiedDI.registerIf(Analytics.self,","                     condition: isProd,","                     factory: { FirebaseAnalytics() },","                     fallback: { NoOpAnalytics() })","","\/\/ 스코프 등록 (동기)","UnifiedDI.registerScoped(UserService.self, scope: .session) { UserServiceImpl() }","","\/\/ 스코프 등록 (비동기)","UnifiedDI.registerAsyncScoped(ProfileCache.self, scope: .screen) {","    await ProfileCache.make()","}"]},{"level":3,"type":"heading","text":"해결(Resolution)","anchor":"%ED%95%B4%EA%B2%B0Resolution"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["\/\/ 옵셔널 해결","let s1: Service? = UnifiedDI.resolve(Service.self)","","\/\/ 필수 해결 (미등록 시 fatalError)","let s2: Service = UnifiedDI.requireResolve(Service.self)","","\/\/ throws 기반 해결","let s3: Service = try UnifiedDI.resolveThrows(Service.self)","","\/\/ 기본값과 함께 해결","let s4: Service = UnifiedDI.resolve(Service.self, default: MockService())","","\/\/ 비동기 해결","let s5: Service? = await UnifiedDI.resolveAsync(Service.self)"]},{"level":3,"type":"heading","text":"해제(Release)","anchor":"%ED%95%B4%EC%A0%9CRelease"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["\/\/ 타입 해제","UnifiedDI.release(Service.self)","","\/\/ 전체 해제 (테스트\/디버그 용도)","await UnifiedDI.releaseAll()","","\/\/ 스코프 전체 해제","UnifiedDI.releaseScope(.session, id: userID)","","\/\/ 특정 타입의 스코프 인스턴스 해제","UnifiedDI.releaseScoped(UserService.self, kind: .session, id: userID)"]},{"level":3,"type":"heading","text":"팁(Tips)","anchor":"%ED%8C%81Tips"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"스코프: "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".screen"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".session"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".request"},{"type":"text","text":" 제공. 수명주기에 맞춰 "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ScopeContext.shared.setCurrent\/clear"},{"type":"text","text":"를 사용하세요."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"비동기 싱글톤: "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GlobalUnifiedRegistry.registerAsyncSingleton(Type.self) { await ... }"},{"type":"text","text":" 패턴으로 최초 1회 생성 후 재사용합니다."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"그래프 자동 수집(선택): ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CircularDependencyDetector.shared.setAutoRecordingEnabled(true)"},{"text":" 설정 시, 해석 경로에서 자동으로 의존 엣지를 기록합니다.","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"type":"thematicBreak"},{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"DI (단순화 API)","anchor":"DI-%EB%8B%A8%EC%88%9C%ED%99%94-API"},{"level":3,"type":"heading","text":"등록(Registration)","anchor":"%EB%93%B1%EB%A1%9DRegistration"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["\/\/ 기본 등록","DI.register(Service.self) { ServiceImpl() }","","\/\/ 조건부 등록","DI.registerIf(Service.self, condition: flag,","              factory: { RealService() },","              fallback: { MockService() })","","\/\/ 스코프 등록 (동기\/비동기)","DI.registerScoped(UserService.self, scope: .request) { UserServiceImpl() }","DI.registerAsyncScoped(RequestContext.self, scope: .request) { await RequestContext.create() }"]},{"level":3,"type":"heading","text":"해결(Resolution)","anchor":"%ED%95%B4%EA%B2%B0Resolution"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["let d1: Service? = DI.resolve(Service.self)","let d2: Result<Service, DIError> = DI.resolveResult(Service.self)","let d3: Service = try DI.resolveThrows(Service.self)"]},{"type":"heading","level":3,"anchor":"%ED%95%B4%EC%A0%9CRelease","text":"해제(Release)"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["DI.release(Service.self)","DI.releaseScope(.request, id: requestID)","DI.releaseScoped(UserService.self, kind: .request, id: requestID)"]},{"type":"aside","style":"note","name":"참고","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"심볼 링크는 공개(public) API에 대해서만 자동 노출됩니다. DI의 일부 메서드는 모듈 외부 노출이 아니면 문서 심볼 목록에 보이지 않을 수 있습니다. 문서의 예제 코드를 참고하시거나, 외부 사용이 필요하면 public으로 승격하는 것을 고려하세요."